# 🔐 Data Privacy Awareness Website

This project is a simple and interactive website that spreads awareness about data privacy and online safety.

## 🚀 Features

* Modern UI with gradient design
* Animated sections and hover effects
* Information about cyber threats and protection
* Fully responsive layout

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* Font Awesome Icons

## 📚 Purpose

This project was created as a college assignment to educate users about the importance of protecting personal data online.

